          <title>Zuckerberg Announces Changes to Facebook Content Moderation</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Meta CEO Mark Zuckerberg announces changes to content moderation on Facebook and Instagram, shifting from fact-checking to user-written community notes, in a move seen as an attempt to appease the incoming Trump administration.]]></description>
